60 Pītisahagataduka, Kusalattika
Pītisahagataduka, Kusalattika
69.
191Pītisahagataṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca napītisahagato nakusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… . Hetuyā tīṇi…pe…  avigate tīṇi.
192Pītisahagataṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca napītisahagato naakusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā… . Hetuyā tīṇi…pe…  avigate tīṇi. (Abyākatamūlaṃ tīṇiyeva paccayavasena.)
